# ============================================================
# Global .dockerignore for His.Hope monorepo
# ============================================================

# --- .NET build artifacts ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/packages/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.cache
*.vspscc

# --- Node.js / Angular ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.angular/
**/coverage/

# --- Git ---
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# --- IDE & Editor ---
**/.idea/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Documentation (large files) ---
**/*.md
!README.md

# --- Test & Coverage ---
**/TestResults/
**/coverlet/
**/coverage/
*.trx
*.testlog

# --- Docker & Kubernetes ---
**/docker-compose.override.yml
**/.env
!.env.example
**/.env.*
!**/*.env.example

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/Logs/

# --- Temp files ---
**/tmp/
**/temp/
**/.tmp/

# --- CI/CD pipeline artifacts ---
**/.tekton/
**/pipeline-runs/

# --- Python (ML services) ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/

# --- Bazel ---
**/bazel-*/
**/.bazelrc.user

# --- Archives ---
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.7z
